sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Contributor
    participant Bot as HR Agent Bot
    participant Claude as Claude API
    participant Sheets as Google Sheets
    participant CC as Core Contributors
    participant Beta as Beta App

    Note over C,Beta: Phase 1: Gate
    C->>Bot: /start
    Bot->>Sheets: Check AuthorizedUsers
    Sheets-->>Bot: authorized ✓

    Note over C,Beta: Phase 2: Discovery
    Bot->>C: "Tell me about yourself"
    C->>Bot: Skills, rate, availability (free text)
    Bot->>Claude: extract_profile (tool use)
    Claude-->>Bot: {name, skills[], rate, commitment%}
    Bot->>Sheets: Save contributor profile

    Note over C,Beta: Phase 3: Matching
    Bot->>Sheets: Get open opportunities
    Sheets-->>Bot: Opportunities list
    Bot->>Bot: Run matching algorithm
    Bot->>C: Top 3 matches with scores [Select]
    C->>Bot: Selects opportunity

    Note over C,Beta: Phase 4: Negotiation
    Bot->>C: "Propose your terms"
    C->>Bot: Rate, commitment, duration
    Bot->>Claude: extract_terms (tool use)
    Claude-->>Bot: {hourlyRate, commitment%, months}
    Bot->>Bot: Calculate settlement likelihood
    Bot->>Sheets: Save draft agreement
    Bot->>C: "Rate: $70/hr, Likelihood: 78% [Submit] [Modify]"
    C->>Bot: Submit

    Note over C,Beta: Phase 5: Multi-Reviewer Aggregation
    Bot->>Sheets: Update status → under_review
    Bot->>CC: DM proposal [Approve/Counter/Reject]
    CC->>Bot: Counter: $65/hr + feedback
    CC->>Bot: Approve + feedback
    Bot->>Claude: Aggregate feedback
    Claude-->>Bot: Synthesized counter-offer
    Bot->>C: "Team suggests $65/hr. Feedback: ..."
    C->>Bot: Accept counter

    Note over C,Beta: Phase 6: Resolution
    Bot->>Sheets: Update status → approved
    Bot->>Beta: POST /orgs/agreement
    Beta-->>Bot: Agreement created
    Bot->>C: "Welcome to the team!"
